al-share-reddit&quot; title=&quot;Reddit&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Reddit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.verdadesign.com%2Fblog%2Flessons-learned-%25E2%2580%2593-developers-view-design&amp;amp;text=Lessons%20Learned%20%E2%80%93%20A%20Developer%26%23039%3Bs%20View%20on%20Design&quot; class=&quot;social-share-twitter&quot; title=&quot;Twitter&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Twitter&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
